cards.name: Soulful Singer
cards.shortData:
Maestro has such a wonderful and soothing voice. When you listen to her sing , it calms you down instantly and you fall in love with her voice.

She‚Äôs at her best when she sings for her loved ones. You are the luckiest if you are one of them :-)

cards.name: Graceful Dancer
cards.shortData:
If you know Maestro , you know how good of a dancer she is. She rocks the dance floor anywhere and everywhere. She is the centre of attraction in any dance she is in. Even if there are twenty people dancing or if she is dancing in a corner, you will not fail to notice her.The way she carries her smile throughout , the expressions ( lot of fans for that) and the way she completely enjoys dancing , you just can‚Äôt beat that.

She‚Äôs the best of the best. Vessel washing dance is a new dance form , for which the maestro herself holds the patent.

cards.name: Talented Artist
cards.shortData:
Maestro‚Äôs talents does not stop at singing and dancing. She play loads of instruments and is quite good at it too. Maestro is the perfect example of a multi talented person. Is there anything she can‚Äôt do? Only time will tell ;-)

We are all waiting for the day where she releases a video as ‚ÄúMusic by, Song by, Sung By and Danced by‚Äù - Maestro

cards.name: Dutiful Daughter
cards.shortData:
She‚Äôs the world‚Äôs best daughter. You see people remembering how special their parents are just on Mother‚Äôs day or Father‚Äôs day and expressing it in social media. She does that too, but she knows how special her parents are all throughout the year.‚Ä®She understands the sacrifices and hardships they had to go through to raise her and her brother . And she is grateful for that and displays that.

She understands the trust her parents have on her and the freedom that they have given and supported , and she never breaks their trust.

cards.name: Loyal Sister
cards.shortData:
Only a handful of us are lucky enough to have a sibling , who will not rat you out to your parents just for the fun of it :-p Her brother is one such lucky sibling. Not only did she not rat him out when she found he had a girlfriend , she kept his secret for years and stood loyal to his sibling.

She is his secret-keeper.

cards.name: Friend You Can Count On
cards.shortData:
She is everything anyone , anyone , could hope their friend could be. You can trust her to be there for you anytime you need her. She‚Äôll go out of her way to make you feel special and heard and noticed . There will never be a boring moment when she‚Äôs around. The respect she gives to the value of Friendship is something that‚Äôs lost in a lot of people today.

Count yourself the luckiest person in the world , if maestro calls you her friend. You have a someone standing by you, in every good and bad thing in your life :-)

cards.name: Enemy to None
cards.shortData: If there is a reward to find a person who hates Maestro , it will be for an unfathomable amount. Do you know why? They would be confident that you‚Äôll never be able to claim the reward. It‚Äôs impossible to find someone like that. Even the person who detests everything will lose all their defence in front of her innocence and sincerity towards them

cards.name: Loved by All
cards.shortData:
Maestro makes friends wherever she goes , be it a wedding where she talks to a completely new woman , or joining a new team at work or a dance crew or even a visit to the RTO ( she made three friends in one day there ) . There is something about her that makes people trust her at once.

She has made so many friends , that sometimes tough to keep track of how many friends she have. There are even people who consider her a friend :-p that she is not even aware of.

Maestro avlo popular.

cards.name: Passionate Student
cards.shortData:
What would you describe a child , who even after the car she was travelling in ran into a problem, was worried only about getting to school on time :-p While the rest of the children are praying for a miracle so that they don‚Äôt go to school .

That child grew into our Maestro :-p she‚Äôll never miss college, not sleep during a boring class and never sits past the second bench. Like everything else, she‚Äôs passionate about studies too and gives in her one hundred percent , and if possible more.

cards.name: Master Chef
cards.shortData:
What happens when the maestro gets bored? She sprouts out a new talent :-p As if she isn‚Äôt the best at enough things already , she has stepped into the world of cooking , starting with baking :-p And we can see for ourselves that it‚Äôs something that comes to her easily ( we are not lucky enough to taste her cooking yet)

After all, she does have a database of Masterchef Australia episodes in her head and amma‚Äôs foolproof recipies :)

cards.name: Confident Speaker
cards.shortData:
‚ÄúAre you kidding me?Come on already!!‚Äù. Yes , she can do this too :-) She can effortlessly go on stage and impress people. This time on , it isn‚Äôt with her dance or song. She can captivate you just with her speech.

Although she can captivate us , just by sitting with us at a table , and talking , just about anything. Going in front of an audience and having their attention for the whole time , is no easy feat. And time and time on, maestro has proved she is well capable of that

cards.name: Core√≥grafa
cards.shortData:
Maestro‚Äôs interest in dance doesn‚Äôt just stop at participating in cultural or dancing to cover videos. You can see her full of life , when she is organising a small dance with her family or friends for a wedding. She will spend many sleepless nights towards making the once in a lifetime occasion of her loved ones special , in her style. And if you had the opportunity to see the end fruits of her toil, you‚Äôll know how her energy and enthusiasm gets passed on to whoever dances with her. Already she has had many requests for organising dances ;-)
And with the experience she has gained from organising these group dances , she has now moved on to doing her own choreos. Everyone is waiting to see the heights that she‚Äôs going to achieve.

cards.name: The GoTo Person
cards.shortData:
You are at crossroads in life and not sure what to do? Go to Maestro.
You have a problem in your relationship and not sure how to solve it? Go to Maestro.
You are stuck in coding , and not sure what the solution is ? Go to Maestro.
You are bored, and can‚Äôt decide which movie or series is worth your time? Go to Maestro

Basically Maestro is the ‚ÄúIdea Mani‚Äù of our circle. There is nothing she doesn‚Äôt have answers to . But even in a rare case where she doesn‚Äôt , she will make you feel capable enough to find the solution yourself. It‚Äôs her superpower.
